{"tid":1945660,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國YouTuber狂舔馬桶挑戰武漢肺炎成功 順利確診","createTime":"2020-03-27T08:09:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T08:48:30.000Z","uid":41343,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"91699f509032c2137df450745ac6b3da1abd738d","tid":1945660,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T08:09:25.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情大流行，竟還有趁勢想紅！一名美國YouTuber日前在推特上接受女網紅路易絲（Ava Louise）的「舔馬桶挑戰」要挑戰新冠病毒，於是拍下仿效影片，跑到公廁裡狂舔馬桶，沒想到隔幾天就爆出確診，遭到網友狂罵「白痴活該！」<br />\n<br />\n據Usa Today Sun報導，影片中，這名網紅Larz走入一間公廁，接著直接跪在地上，沒有猶豫地伸出舌頭舔了馬桶邊緣的污漬，時間長達8秒；結束後還對著鏡頭大笑，一付沒什麼的表情說：「不會有事的。」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n影片上傳超過500百萬人觀看，沒想到隔幾天就上傳一張躺在病床上的照片，自爆事後覺得身體不舒服，到醫院做篩檢，結果為陽性反應，確診新冠肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n對此，網友一點也不感到同情，紛紛砲轟他自食惡果，「恭喜你挑戰成功」、「想紅什麼都做的出來」、「病得不輕」、「白痴活該」。目前他的帳號已關閉，影片也全部下架。（艾以琳/綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kairos.news/184991\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkairos.news%2F184991&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNsg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=0432fc3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://kairos.news/184991</a>"},{"pid":"6021eeb2503cc6f649f805137d414f04ff756728","tid":1945660,"uid":14065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T08:11:21.000Z","msg":"求仁得仁"},{"pid":"e90ceb8ba09bbf1b69eb919ba0bb8369ba55fe90","tid":1945660,"uid":61032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T08:12:40.000Z","msg":"痴撚線奶馬桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fed8bdc4de0b3bc94f105ae48ebbe742350c35e","tid":1945660,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T08:17:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg